select SUM( CASE WHEN status = 1 THEN amount END) as depositAmount, DATE_FORMAT(created_at,'%M') as months from `deposits` where year(`created_at`) >= '2021' group by MONTH(created_at) order by `created_at` asc

select SUM( CASE WHEN status = 1 THEN amount END) as withdrawAmount, DATE_FORMAT(created_at,'%M') as months from `withdrawals` where year(`created_at`) >= '2021' and `status` = 1 group by MONTH(created_at) order by `created_at` asc
select sum(amount)   as totalAmount, DATE(created_at) day from `withdrawals` where `created_at` >= '2022-02-07 13:30:26' and `status` = 1 group by `day`
select `browser`, `os`, `country` from `user_logins` where date(`created_at`) >= '2022-02-07'
